<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Create Product - Scatch Admin</title>
    <%- include('./partials/theme-head') %>
</head>

<body class="premium-shell min-h-screen font-sans antialiased">
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <% if (typeof success !=='undefined' && success && success.length> 0) { %>
        <div class="fixed left-1/2 top-24 z-50 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 shadow-lg">
            <%= success %>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
        <section class="premium-card mb-8 p-8 sm:p-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
                <div>
                    <p class="premium-muted mb-3">Product Builder</p>
                    <h1 class="premium-title">Launch a new premium bag with confidence.</h1>
                    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-stone-600">The creation flow now matches the elevated storefront, with cleaner sections, stronger readability, and a more boutique admin feel.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/owners/admin" class="premium-btn-light">Back to Inventory</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[280px_minmax(0,1fr)]">
            <aside class="premium-card h-fit p-6">
                <p class="premium-muted mb-4">Dashboard</p>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-sm font-medium">
                    <a class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-primary" href="/owners/admin"><i class="ri-box-3-line"></i> All Products</a>
                    <a class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-stone-950 px-4 py-3 text-white" href="/owners/products/create"><i class="ri-add-circle-line"></i> Create New Product</a>
                    <a class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 transition hover:bg-white hover:text-primary" href="/owners/manage"><i class="ri-user-settings-line"></i> Manage Profile</a>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-8 rounded-[1.5rem] bg-stone-950 p-5 text-white">
                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-stone-400">Tips</p>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-stone-300">Use balanced color pairs so each product card feels intentional and premium in the storefront grid.</p>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <section class="premium-card p-8 sm:p-10">
                <div class="mb-8 border-b border-stone-200/70 pb-6">
                    <p class="premium-muted mb-2">Create Product</p>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-stone-900">Add a new premium bag</h2>
                </div>

                <form autocomplete="off" action="/products/create" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/75 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Product Information</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-stone-500">Start with the core details your customers will see first.</p>

                        <div class="mt-6">
                            <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Product Image</label>
                            <input name="image" type="file" required class="premium-input file:mr-4 file:rounded-full file:border-0 file:bg-stone-950 file:px-5 file:py-3 file:text-sm file:font-semibold file:text-white hover:file:bg-primary">
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Product Name</label>
                                <input name="name" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Classic Tote" required class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Price (₹)</label>
                                <input name="price" type="number" placeholder="2500" required class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Discount Price (₹)</label>
                                <input name="discount" type="number" placeholder="200" class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/70 bg-white/75 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Styling Configuration</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-stone-500">Use hex values like `#ffffff` to shape the storefront presentation.</p>

                        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Background Color</label>
                                <input name="bgcolor" type="text" placeholder="#f0f0f0" required class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Panel Color</label>
                                <input name="panelcolor" type="text" placeholder="#ffffff" required class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700">Text Color</label>
                                <input name="textcolor" type="text" placeholder="#000000" required class="premium-input">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                        <button type="submit" class="premium-btn !py-3.5">
                            <i class="ri-check-line"></i> Create Product
                        </button>
                        <a href="/owners/admin" class="premium-btn-light">Cancel</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </section>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
